Definition: the act of sustaining life by food or providing a means of subsistence
Example: they were in want of sustenance; fishing was their main sustainment
Synonyms: verb, stative, sustain, sustentation, adj, pert, sustentacular, sustainment, consumption, maintenance, maintain, upkeep, support, the, act, of, sustaining, life, by, food, or, providing, a, means, subsistence, they, were, in, want, fishing, was, their, main
Category: noun.act
